  "body": "It looks like currently we are trying to remove staging directory when `NodeStage` call errors out/times out - https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/c58767b1e2981bd7826b4336de0c2756fa975339/pkg/volume/csi/csi_attacher.go#L331\r\n\r\nThis is problematic because in case of timeout, the staging path might still be in-use by the driver for staging the volumes and k8s may unilaterally remove it.  I think similar problem exists for mount code too. We will have to treat timeout errors differently.\r\n\r\ncc @vladimirvivien @msau42 @kubernetes/sig-storage-bugs \r\n\r\n/sig storage\r\n\r\n\r\n",
